Ururka Caafimaadka ee Qaramada Midoobay wuxuu ku dhawaaqay COVID-19 inuu yahay cudur faafa
Arbacada, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) wuxuu ku dhawaaqay in cudurka COVID-19 ee hadda jira ee ka dhashay coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 uu yahay cudur faafa.
Inkastoo ereyga "Cudurku" uu si weyn u tixraacayo sida cudurku u gaadhay dalal badan, laakiin aan si gaar ah u tixraacin baaxadda uu u yahay, WHO waxay tilmaantay muhiimadda ay leedahay in dawladuhu ka qaybqaataan la dagaalanka:
"Dunida oo dhan waxay beddeli kartaa halka uu cudurku u socdo.
