Cudurka faafa ee 201920 waa cudurka faafa ee hadda jira ee 2019Covid-19 (COVID-19), kaas oo ay keento cudurka faafa ee SARS-CoV-2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Bishii Diseembar 2019, cudurka ayaa laga ogaaday Wuhan, Shiinaha; Janaayo 30, 2020, waxaa loo shaaciyay masiibo caafimaad oo khatar ah oo caalami ah, iyo Maarso 11, 2020, waxaa loo shaaciyay cudur faafa.
Ilaa iyo 10 April 2020, ku dhawaad 1.61 milyan oo qof ayaa ku dhacay COVID-19 210 dal iyo gobol, oo ku dhawaad 97,000 ay dhinteen.
