Qaar ka mid ah saraakiisha Mareykanka iyo saxafiyiinta ayaa ku dhaliilay Mareykanka oo ka gaabsaday soo dejinta Shiinaha qalabka lagama maarmaanka u ah, oo ay ku jiraan qalabka caafimaadka ee aasaasiga ah.
Safarada diyaaradaha ayaa lagu falanqeeyey si loo ogaado loona qorsheeyo faafitaanka cudurka waxaana lagu soo warramay joornaalka The Journal of Travel Medicine bartamihii Janaayo 2020.
Iyada oo ku saleysan xogta 2018 ee ay soo saartay Ururka Safarka Diyaaradaha (IATA), Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo iyo Taipei waxay la kulmeen tiro badan oo safrayaal ah oo ka imanaya Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney, iyo Melbourne ayaa sidoo kale lagu sheegay inay yihiin kuwa ugu caansan ee booqda Wuhan.
Bali ayaa lagu tilmaamay mid ka mid ah 20ka magaalo ee ugu soo booqan ee aan si fiican u diyaar garoobin cudurka faafa, halka magaalooyinka Australia ay si fiican u diyaar garoobaan.
Waxa uu sheegay in wax badan laga baaro COVID-19, iyo in Australia ay diiradda saareyso kormeerka xuduudaha iyo isweydaarsiga macluumaadka ka dhanka ah cudurka faafa.
Bishii Maarso 21, Australia waxay ku dhawaaqday sharci ka hortagga fayraska iyo ilaalinta bulshada.
Iyada oo la raacayo natiijooyinka ka soo baxaya joojinta safarka dadweynaha ee Wuhan, Hubei, dalal badan ayaa qorsheynaya inay ka soo qaadaan muwaadiniintooda iyo diblomaasiyadooda, inta badan iyagoo adeegsanaya diyaaradaha dibedda ee dalkooda, iyadoo hay'adaha Shiinaha ay siiyaan dukumiintiyada loo baahan yahay.
Kanada, Mareykanka, Japan, Hindiya, Sri Lanka, Australia, Faransiiska, Argentina, Jarmalka iyo Thailand ayaa ka mid ah waddamada ugu horreeya ee diyaar u ah inay ka soo guuraan muwaadiniintooda.
Pakistan ayaa sheegtay inaysan dib u soo celin doonin dadka ay ka soo guureyso Shiinaha.
Beriyaas ayaa 7kii Febraayo ku soo celiyay 34 qof oo reer Brazil ah ama qoysas marka lagu daro afar qof oo reer Poland ah, Shiine iyo Hindi.
Dadka reer Poland, Shiinaha iyo Hindiya ayaa loo wareejiyay diyaarado ay ku tagaan Poland, halkaasoo diyaaradda Brazil ay joogsatay wax yar ka hor inta aysan sii wadin safarka ay ku sii jeeddo Brazil.
Dadka reer Brazil ee u soo baxay Wuhan ayaa lagu soo rogay xarun ciidan oo ku taal meel u dhow magaalada Brasília.
Maalintaas, 215 oo reer Kanada ah (176 duulimaad oo hore iyo 39 duulimaad oo labaad oo ay bixiso dowladda Mareykanka) ayaa laga soo diray Wuhan oo loo diray CFB Trenton si loo soo celiyo laba toddobaad.
Febraayo 11, diyaarad kale oo 185 qof oo reer Canada ah ay la socdeen oo ka soo jeeday Wuhan ayaa ku dhacday CFB Trenton.
Febraayo 3 iyo 4, masuuliyiinta Australia waxay 277 qof u geeyeen xabsiga Christmas Island, oo loo beddelay meel lagu xiro 14 maalmood.
Diyaaraddii ku soo laabtay New Zealand ayaa gaadhay garoonka diyaaradaha ee Auckland 5kii Febraayo; dadka saarnaa (oo ay ku jiraan kuwa ka yimid Australia iyo Jasiiradaha Baasifigga) ayaa lagu soo rogay saldhigga ciidamada ee Whangaparoa, waqooyiga Auckland.
Bishii Febraayo 15, Mareykanka ayaa ku dhawaaqay inuu dib u soo celiyo Maraykanada ku jira Diamond Princess.
Febraayo 21, diyaarad ay la socdeen 129 rakaab ah oo reer Canada ah oo ka soo baxday Diamond Princess ayaa ku dhacday Trenton, Ontario.
Bilowgii Maarso, dowladda Hindiya waxay bilaabeen inay dadka ay ka soo qaadaan Iiraan. 14-kii Maarso, diyaarad ay bixiso dowladda South African Airways ayaa soo qaadday dadka Koonfur Afrika 112.
Imtixaanka caafimaad ayaa markii ugu horreysay la sameeyay, iyadoo afar qof oo reer Koonfur Afrika ah ay muujiyeen calaamado koronto oo lagu soo bandhigay halista.
Koonfur Afrika oo kaliya ayaa la soo saaray oo aan calaamado lahayn.
Natiijada baaritaanka ayaa muujisay in dhammaan dadka reer Koonfur Afrika, oo ay ku jiraan shaqaalaha duulimaadyada, duuliyeyaasha, shaqaalaha hoteelka iyo ciidamada ka shaqeeya adeegyada gargaarka, si ammaan ah loo kormeero oo loo qoondeeyo 14 maalmood oo ka mid ah xarunta The Ranch Resort.
Bishii Maarso 20aad, Mareykanka ayaa bilaabay inuu dib u soo celiyo qayb ka mid ah ciidamada ku sugan Ciraaq sababo la xiriira cudurka faafa.
Bishii Febraayo 5, Wasaaradda Arrimaha Dibadda ee Shiinaha ayaa sheegtay in 21 dal (oo ay ku jiraan Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad & Tobago, Masar iyo Iran) ay deeq u direen Shiinaha.
Qaar ka mid ah ardayda Chinese ee ku jira jaamacadaha Mareykanka ayaa ku biiray dadaal ay ku caawiyaan inay gacan ka geystaan rarka gargaarka ee qaybaha cudurka faafa ee Shiinaha, halkaas oo koox weyn oo ku taal Chicago ay soo aruurisay ilaa 50,000 oo maaskaro N95 ah oo loo dhiibay Isbitaalada Gobolka Hubei bishii Janaayo 30. Ururka gargaarka ee Direct Relief, oo kaashanaya FedEx, ayaa u diray 200,000 maaskaro iyo dharka kale ee ilaalinaya, oo ay ku jiraan dharka iyo dharka, oo lagu qaaday diyaarad gaar ah oo loo qaaday Isbitaalka Wuhan Union bishii Janaayo 30.
Febraayo 5, Bill iyo Melinda Gates waxay ku dhawaaqeen inay bixiyeen $ 100 milyan oo doolar hay'adda caafimaadka adduunka si ay u caawiyaan cilmi baarista tallaalka iyo daaweynta iyo ilaalinta "dadka ugu halista badan ee Afrika iyo Aasiya".
Telefishanka Interaction ayaa sheegay in dowladda Shiinaha ay 200 000 waji dabool ah u siisay Filibiin 6-dii Febraayo, kadib markii Senator Richard Gordon uu 3.16 milyan oo waji dabool ah u diray Wuhan.
Febraayo 19, Laanqeyrta Cas ee Singapore ayaa ku dhawaaqday inay Shiinaha u dirayso $2.26 milyan oo deeq ah.
Japan waxay soo bandhigtay 1 milyan oo maaskaro ah Wuhan, Turkiga waxay soo dhoofiyeen qalab caafimaad, Ruushka wuxuu soo dhoofiyay 1 milyan oo tan oo dheeraad ah oo maaskaro ah Wuhan, Malaysia waxay ku dhawaaqday inay soo bandhigtay 18 milyan oo maaskaro ah Shiinaha, Jarmalku wuxuu soo bandhigay qalab caafimaad oo kala duwan oo ay ku jiraan 10,000 oo dharka difaaca ee loogu talagalay iyo Mareykanka wuxuu u soo bandhigay Shiinaha 17.8 tan oo maaskaro caafimaad oo uu ballanqaaday inuu sii doono 100 milyan oo dollar oo dheeraad ah si loo caawiyo dhaqaalaha dalalka kale ee cudurka faafa. Tirada cudurka faafa ee Shiinaha ayaa hoos u dhacday, iyadoo dalkaasi u dirayo caawiyaha caalamiga ah ee cudurka faafa.
Bishii Maarso, Shiinaha, Cuba iyo Ruushka ayaa u diray qalab caafimaad iyo khabiiro si ay uga caawiyaan Talyaaniga inay la tacaalaan cudurka faafa ee coronavirus.
Dhaqaale-bixiye Jack Ma ayaa 1.1 milyan oo qalab lagu baarayo cudurada, 6 milyan oo maaskaro ah iyo 60,000 oo dharka difaaca ah u diray Addis Abeba, Ethiopia si ay u faafiyaan Midowga Afrika.
Kadib wuxuu Panama u diray 5,000 qalab oo baaritaan ah, 100,000 maaskaro iyo 5 mashiinada neefsashada.
Ma waxay sidoo kale siisay Kanada qalab caafimaad. Nederland, Spain, Turkey, Georgia, iyo Czech Republic ayaa ka walaacsan yihiin maaskaro iyo qalab baaritaan oo laga sameeyay Shiinaha.
Tusaale ahaan, Spain waxay joojisay isticmaalka 58,000 oo ka mid ah qalabka baaritaanka cudurka ee Shiinaha oo leh 30% saxnaanta, halka Nederland ay ka saartay 600,000 oo maaskaro ah oo Shiinaha ah sababtoo ah waxay ahaayeen kuwo daciif ah.
Belgium ayaa ka saartay 100,000 oo maaskaro ah oo aan la isticmaalin, waxaana la rumeysan yahay inay ka yimaadeen Shiinaha, laakiin waxay asal ahaan ka yimaadeen Colombia.
Dhinaca kale, deeqda Shiinaha ayaa si wanaagsan loogu soo dhaweeyay qaybo ka mid ah Koonfurta Ameerika iyo Afrika. 2da Abriil, Bangiga Adduunka ayaa bilaabay hawlgalka gargaarka degdegga ah ee dalalka soo koraya.
Ururka Caafimaadka ee Qaramada Midoobay ayaa bogaadiyay dadaalka ay hoggaamiyeyaasha Shiinaha ku qaadeen xakamaynta iyo ka hortagga cudurka faafa.
Ururka Caafimaadka ee Qaramada Midoobay ayaa sheegay in ay jirto kala duwanaansho u dhexeeya cudurka SARS ee 2002-2004, oo ay mas'uuliyiinta Shiinaha ku eedeeyeen inay sirta ku hayaan oo ay xakameynayaan tallaabooyinka ka hortagga iyo xakamaynta, iyo cudurka hadda jira ee ay dowladdu "u soo saartay macluumaad joogto ah si ay u siiyaan cabsi ka hor inta aan la fasaxin Sannadka Cusub".
23-kii Janaayo, ka dib go'aanka maamulka sare ee dhaqan gelinta go'aanka joojinta Wuhan, wakiilka Ururka Caafimaadka ee Qaramada Midoobay Gauden Galea ayaa sheegay in inkastoo "aan ahayn talo soo jeedin WHO ah", ay sidoo kale ahayd "caadiyad xooggan oo ka mid ah rabitaanka ka hortagga cudurka faafa ee hadda jira" wuxuuna ugu yeeray "wax aan horay loo arag taariikhda caafimaadka guud". 30-kii Janaayo, ka dib markii la xaqiijiyay in cudurrada ka soo galaya dadka ka baxsan Shiinaha iyo tirada cudurrada sii kordhaya ee dalalka, Ururka Caafimaadka Midoobay wuxuu ku dhawaaqay cudurka faafa inay tahay dhibaato caafimaad oo guud oo u eg cudurka faafa ee MICP, kaas oo ah cudurka cudurka cudurka cudurka ee lixaad ee ka dhacay dalalka kale ee dalka Shiinaha.
Agaasimaha guud ee Ururka Caafimaadka ee Qaramada Midoobay Tedros Adhanom ayaa sheegay in PHEIC ay sabab u tahay khatarta faafitaanka adduunka, gaar ahaan dalalka saboolka ah iyo kuwa dhaqaalaha yar yar ee aan haysan hay'ado caafimaad oo xoog leh.
Marka la eego hirgelinta xayiraadaha safarka, Tedros wuxuu sheegay in " aysan jirin baahi loo qabo in la sameeyo tallaabooyin aan loo baahnayn oo xannibaadda ku ah dhaqdhaqaaqa dadka iyo ganacsiga " iyo in " WHO aysan u baahnayn in la sameeyo xayiraad ganacsi iyo safar".
Febraayo 5, WHO waxay dalwaday dalalka inay bixiyaan $ 675 milyan si ay u taageeraan tallaabooyinka diyaarinta cudurka faafa ee dalalka saboolka ah, iyadoo sheegtay in ay tahay mid deg deg ah in la taageero dalalka "oo leh barnaamijyo gaar ah oo lagu ogaado dadka qaba fayraska, xitaa haddii ay soo baxaan".
Tedros wuxuu sidoo kale ku dhawaaqay in "dhammaanteen aan awood u leenahay sida daciifnimada" wuxuuna dalbaday waddamada inay "maalgashiga maanta sameeyaan ama ay lacag badan ka bixiyaan ka dib". Febraayo 11, wareysi saxaafadeed, WHO waxay xaqiijisay in COVID-19 ay tahay magaca cudurka.
Maalintaas, Tedros wuxuu ku dhawaaqay in Xoghayaha Guud ee Qaramada Midoobay António Guterres uu ogolaaday inuu "ku dadaalo sida ugu badan ee Qaramada Midoobay u jawaabi karto".
Sidaa darteed waxaa la aasaasay Kooxda Caafimaadka ee Qaramada Midoobay, oo isku xirta dhammaan howlaha Qaramada Midoobay, taas oo ay sheegtay in ay "laftiisa u dhigi doonto in ay diiradda saareyso gargaarka caafimaadka iyadoo la adeegsanayo laamaha kale ee la xiriira khibradooda la xidhiidha saameynta bulshada, dhaqaalaha, iyo horumarka guud ee masiibada".
14-kii Febraayo, Kooxda Wadajirka ah ee WHO ayaa la sameeyay Shiinaha si ay u soo xulato khubarada caalamiga ah iyo WHO ee loo diray Shiinaha si ay uga caawiyaan xakamaynta iyo xakamaynta cudurka iyo faafitaanka cudurka" iyagoo tababar iyo la-talin la siinaya hay'adaha muhiimka ah ee dalka iyo booqasho goobo kala duwan si loo falanqeeyo "saameeyaha ka hortagga cudurka ee gobollada iyo gobollada oo ay ku jiraan qaybaha caafimaadka iyo magaalooyinka". 25-kii Febraayo, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday in "dunidu ay tahay inay wax ka qabato diyaarinta cudurka faafa", iyadoo ku dhawaaqday in ay tahay waqti hore in la ogaado in cudurka coronavirus uu bilaabmi karo, laakiin in ay "u diyaarinayo" heerka caalamiga ah.
Si looga hortago cudurka faafa ee sii kordhaya ee Iiraan, WHO waxay u dirtay koox wadajir ah si ay u falanqeeyaan xaaladda. 28kii Febraayo, saraakiisha WHO waxay sheegeen in baaritaanka cudurka faafa ee caalamiga ah laga kordhin doono heerka "ugu sarreeya" ilaa heerka "ugu sarreeya", taas oo ah heerka ugu sarreeya ee digniinta iyo qiimeynta saameynta.
Mike Ryan, oo ah agaasimaha guud ee barnaamijyada gargaarka ee WHO, ayaa ka digay dadka, "Tani waa heerka dhabta ah ee dal kasta oo adduunka ah: Soo kac.
Fayraska ayaa soo dhowaanaya waana inaad diyaar u noqotaan", ayuu ku nuuxnuuxsaday in tallaabooyin adag oo la dagaalanka ah ay ka caawin karaan ka hortagga "halista".
Ryan wuxuu intaas ku daray in wararka la helay aysan dhicin hay'adaha caafimaadka bulshada inay ku dhawaaqaan cudurka faafa adduunka, isagoo sheegay in ku dhawaaqida ay ka dhigan tahay "in aan dhab ahaantii aaminsanahay in qof kasta oo adduunka ah uu ku dhici doono cudurka".
Bishii Maarso 11, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday coronavirus inay tahay cudur faafa.
Agaasimaha Guud ayaa sheegay in WHO ay "ka walaacsan tahay kororka xawaaraha sare iyo tallaabo la'aanta". WHO ayaa si weyn u dhaleeceysay tallaabooyinka ka hortagga cudurka faafa ee la arki karo ee aan la hubin, sida bayaanka ku saabsan masiibada caafimaadka guud iyo cudurrada faafa ee fayraska.
Diidmada ayaa waxaa ka mid ah codsi uu ku baaqay in Agaasimaha Guud ee WHO Tedros Adhanom uu is casiliyo illaa 6ka Abriil, codsigan oo ay saxiixdeen 733,000 oo qof.
Bishii Maarso 26, 2020, khubarada xuquuqda aadanaha ee Qaramada Midoobay waxay ku adkeysteen in la ixtiraamo xuquuqda qof walba inta lagu jiro masiibada COVID-19.
Kooxda khubarada ayaa sheegtay in qof walba uu xaq u leeyahay dhaqdhaqaaq caafimaad oo ah masuuliyad dowladda.
Kooxdu waxay ku adkeysay in la'aanta maalgelinta ama caymiska caafimaadka aysan marnaba noqon doonin sabab loogu kala soocayo koox gaar ah.
Khubarada ayaa ku adkeeyay in qof walba uu xaq u leeyahay caafimaadka, oo ay ku jiraan naafada, dadka ku nool kooxaha dhaqdhaqaaqa, dadka waaweyn, dadka guryahooda ka soo baxay, dadka hoy la'aanta ah, dadka saboolka ah, dadka xabsiga ku jira, iyo qaxootiga iyo kooxaha kale ee aan khaaska ahayn ee u baahan caawimaad dawladeed.
Ururada caalamiga ah iyo dawladaha ayaa la shaqeeya si ay u xaliyaan dhibaatooyinka dhaqaale iyo bulshada ee ka dhashay cudurka faafa ee COVID-19.
Ururka Iskaashiga Dhaqaalaha iyo Horumarinta ayaa bilaabay bog si loo bixiyo macluumaad dhammaystiran oo ku habboon siyaasadaha ka jawaabaya arrintan dalalka adduunka, iyo fikrado iyo talooyin kala duwan.
Laga soo bilaabo siyaasadaha xoojinta caafimaadka iyo dhaqaalaha adduunka si looga hortago saameynta nidaamka guryaha iyo yareynta socodka dadka, tallaabooyinka tiknoolajiyada ah ee la qaaday waxaa ka mid ah Nidaamka raadinta cudurka, iyo sidoo kale si loo caawiyo waddamada inay wax ka bartaan oo ay u caawiyaan inay isu yimaadaan tallaabooyinka caalamiga ah ee la dagaalanka cudurka coronavirus.
Dowladda Shiinaha ayaa waxaa ku dhaliilay Mareykanka, Wasiirka Golaha Wasiirada ee Ingiriiska Michael Gove, iyo Eduardo Bolsonaro, oo ah ina Madaxweynaha Brazil Jair Bolsonaro, sida ay uga jawaabtay cudurka faafa ee ka dhacay gobolka Hubei.
Qaar badan oo ka mid ah madaxda gobolka ee Xisbiga Qaranka ee Shiinaha (CPC) ayaa la eryay sababtoo ah waxay ka hadleen dhibaatada karantiilinta ee Shiinaha dhexe, taas oo muujineysa in aysan ku faraxsanayn tallaabooyinka ay hay'adaha siyaasadeed qaadeen si ay uga hortagaan cudurka faafa ee gobolladaas.
Qaar ka mid ah faallo bixiyeyaasha ayaa sheegay in go'aankaasi uu ahaa mid looga hortago Xoghayaha Guud ee Xisbiga Qaranka Shiinaha Xi Jinping cadhada dadweynaha ee cudurka faafa ee coronavirus.
Qaar ka mid ah madaxda Shiinaha, oo ay ku jiraan Zhao Lijian, ayaa diiday in la ogaado in cudurka faafa ee coronavirus uu ka bilaabmay Wuhan, iyagoo taageeraya fikradaha qaldan ee ku saabsan COVID-19 ee ka imanaya Mareykanka ama Talyaaniga.
Maamulka Donald Trump ee Mareykanka ayaa ugu yeeray coronavirus "virus Shiinaha" ama "virus Wuhan" isagoo sheegay in Shiinaha uu qarinayay macluumaad ka dhigaya in fayraska uu noqdo cudur caalami ah, laakiin waxaa si weyn u diiday qaar ka mid ah dadka inay u arkaan sida takoor iyo in la dhigo mid aan la arki karin in maamulkiisa uu daciif yahay sidii loo hortagi lahaa cudurka faafa.
Shabakadda Daily Beast ayaa heshay warbixin ka timid Dowladda Mareykanka oo ku saabsan tallaabooyinka isgaarsiinta ee laga shakisan yahay inay ka yimaadeen Golaha Amniga Qaranka, halkaas oo tallaabooyinkaasi lagu tilmaamay "Dhammaan waxay ku saabsan yihiin Shiinaha.
Waxaa la noo sheegaa in aan sameyno wax kasta oo aan karanno si aan u faafiyo farriinta meel kasta oo ay ka mid yihiin wareysiyada saxaafadda iyo telefishanka. "Wargeysyada sida Politico, Foreign Policy, iyo Bloomberg waxay muujiyeen in awoodda Shiinaha ee maalgelinta ay tahay hab lagu helo saameyn caalami ah.
Agaasimaha siyaasadda caalamiga ah ee Midowga Yurub Josep Borrell ayaa ka digay in ay jirto dhibaato ku saabsan xiriirka siyaasadeed ee ka dhexeeya dalalka oo ay ku jiraan halganka maamulka caalamiga ah ee muujinta iyo 'siyaasadda samafalka'".
Borrell ayaa sidoo kale sheegay in "Shiinaha uu soo saaray fariin cad oo ah in uu yahay, ka duwan Mareykanka, wada-hawlgalaha ugu fiican ee lagu kalsoonaan karo".
Shiinaha ayaa sidoo kale codsaday in Mareykanka uu ka qaado cunaqabateynta ku saaran Suuriya, Venezuela iyo Iran, iyadoo sidoo kale la sheegay in Shiinaha uu maalgelin u diray Venezuela iyo Iran.
Bishii April 3, Jack Ma wuxuu soo bandhigay 100 000 oo waji-xidh ah oo loo dhiibay Cuba, waxaana la qabtay cunaqabateynta Mareykanka.
Saraakiisha Mareykanka ayaa sidoo kale lagu eedeeyay inay guryahooda ku wareejiyeen maalgelinta caalamiga ah.
Waxaa jira muran kale oo ku saabsan maaskaro oo ka dhashay dalal kale; sida Jarmalka, Austria iyo Switzerland; iyo sidoo kale Czech Republic iyo Talyaaniga.
Turkiga ayaa sidoo kale la wareegay boqolaal mashiinada neefsashada ee Spain u socday.
Bilowgii bishii Maarso, dowladda Talyaaniga ayaa ku eedeysay Midowga Yurub in aysan u muuqan wada shaqeyn Talyaaniga xilli uu ku dhacay cudurka faafa ee coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, safiirka Talyaaniga ee Midowga Yurub ayaa sheegay in "Shiinaha uu ahaa kaalmada kaliya ee Talyaaniga.
Tani dhab ahaantii ma aha calaamad wanaagsan oo ah midnimada Yurub".
Bishii Maarso 22, kadib wadahadal taleefan ah oo uu la yeeshay Ra'iisul Wasaaraha Talyaaniga Giuseppe Conte, Madaxweynaha Ruushka Vladimir Putin ayaa diyaariyey ciidamada Ruushka inay dalka Talyaaniga u diraan ciidamo dhakhaatiir ah, gawaarida jeermiska dila, iyo qalab kale oo caafimaad.
Wargeyska La Stampa ee Talyaaniga ayaa ku tilmaamay "warbixin ka timid madaxweyne sare" oo aan la magacaabin in 80% taageerada Ruushka ay tahay "aan waxtar lahayn ama aan waxtar lahayn Talyaaniga".
Warbixiyaha ayaa ku eedeeyay Ruushka inuu doonayo inuu "xasaasiyad siyaasadeed iyo diblomaasiyadeed" u dhex galo dalalka.
Madaxweynaha Lombardi, Attilio Fontana, iyo Wasiirka Arrimaha Dibadda Talyaaniga, Luigi Di Maio, ayaa diiday warbaahinta iyo waxay muujiyeen inay ku mahadsan yihiin Ruushka.
Ruushka ayaa sidoo kale Mareykanka u diray diyaarad xamuul ah oo ay ku jiraan qalab caafimaad oo la adeegsan karo.
Afhayeenka madaxweynaha Ruushka Dmitry Peskov ayaa yiri: "Ruuxnimadii Putin uu u fidiyay dadka Mareykanka, wuxuu u maleynayaa in marka dadka Mareykanka ay horumariyaan qalabka caafimaadka, ay awoodaan inay na caawiyaan marka ay u baahdaan".
