Mid ka mid ah tijaabooyinka ugu dambeeyay ee PCR ayaa lagu tijaabiyey Charité ee Berlin bishii Janaayo 2020 iyadoo la adeegsanayo nidaamyo deg deg ah oo lagu qabto oo lagu falanqeeyo tijaabooyinka cudurka (rRT-PCR) iyo 250,000 oo qalab oo ay bixiso Ururka Caafimaadka ee Qaramada Midoobay.
Boqortooyada Ingiriiska ayaa sidoo kale diyaarisay baaritaan aan la gaarin 23ka Janaayo 2020. 28ka Janaayo 2020, shirkadda Koonfurta Kuuriya ee Kogenebiotech ayaa diyaarisay tijaabo ah oo loogu talagalay qalab caafimaad oo lagu ogaado SARS-CoV-2 oo ku saleysan PCR (PowerChek Coronavirus).
Waxay baartaa unugyada "E" ee loo yaqaan 'E' ee loo yaqaan 'coronavirus' ee ku jira jirka bini'aadamka, iyo unugyada RdRp ee laga soo bandhigo SARS-CoV-2. Shiinaha, BGI Group waxay ka mid ahayd shirkadaha ugu horreeya ee ay ansixiyeen Hay'adda Qaranka ee Qalabka Caafimaadka si ay u isticmaalaan qalabka baaritaanka SARS CoV-2 ee ku saleysan PCR. Mareykanka, CDC waxay ku sii fidineysaa qalabka RT-PCR Diagnostic ee loo isticmaalo baaritaanka cusub ee Coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV) shaybaarka guud iyada oo loo marayo International Reagent Resource.
