Bishii Maarso 19, 2020, FDA waxay ogolaatay isticmaalka degdegga ah (EUA) ee Abbott Laboratory si ay u tijaabiso Abbott's m2000 system; FDA waxay ogolaatay oggolaansho la mid ah Hologic, LabCorp, iyo Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Bishii Maarso 21, 2020, Cepheid ayaa sidoo kale la siiyay oggolaansho FDA ah in ay isticmaasho nidaamka degdegga ah ee baaritaanka 45 daqiiqo.
