Laga bilaabo 7ka Abriil 2020, kaliya hal baaritaan ayaa FDA-da ansixisay in la sameeyo iyada oo loo marayo oggolaanshaha xaaladaha degdegga ah. Dhamaadka Maarso 2020, Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics iyo Epitope Diagnostic waxay heshay shahaadooyinka Yurub ee qalabkooda baaritaanka, kuwaas oo aqoonsan kara IgG iyo IgA antibodies ee baaritaannada dhiigga.
