Daraasad lagu sameeyay 41 bukaan oo COVID-19, oo lagu dhawaaqay Janaayo 2020 Lancet, ayaa muujisay calaamadaha cudurka oo bilaabay inay muuqdaan 1da Diseembar 2019.
WHO waxay si rasmi ah u sheegtay in calaamadaha cudurka ay bilaabeen inay muuqdaan Diseembar 8, 2019.
