Saddex nooc oo tallaal ah ayaa la baaray.
Marka hore, cilmi baarayaashu waxay rabaan inay sameeyaan tallaal buuxa oo fayraska ah.
Isticmaalka fayraska, ha ahaato mid aan shaqeyn ama dhintay, waxaa loogu talagalay in la kiciyo difaaca jirka ee bini'aadamka si loo ogaado in uu jiro cudur cusub oo COVID-19.
Tallaabada labaad waa isticmaalka unugyada unugyada, taas oo loogu talagalay in la sameeyo tallaal u ogeysiiya difaaca jirka in ay jiraan unugyada fayraska.
Xaaladda SARS-CoV-2, daraasaddan ayaa diiradda saartay dufanka geeska ah ee caawiya fayraska inuu soo galo ACE2.
Habka saddexaad waa habka unugyada (DNA ama RNA, habka cusub ee loo sameeyo tallaalka).
Tallaalkaan ayaa ah mid lagu baaro oo loo baahan yahay in la tijaabiyo saxnaanta iyo awoodda. Bishii Maarso 16, 2020, afar mutadawiciin oo ku sugan Seattle ayaa bilaabay tijaabinta tallaalka.
Tallaalka waxaa ku jira unugyo laga soo qaatay fayraska oo keeni kara cudur. Waxaa la soo jeediyay in la kordhiyo difaaca jirka sida habka ugu wanaagsan ee loo sameeyo tallaalka SARS-COV-2, laakiin weli waxaa jira dhibaato.
Ilaa Abriil 2020 waxaa la sameeyay in ka badan 300 oo tallaal ah.
Toddoba tijaabooyin ayaa lagu sameeyay daawooyinka caadiga ah ee loo oggol yahay daaweynta Malaria, oo ay ku jiraan afar daaweynta hydroxychloroquine ama chloroquine.
Cilmi-baarista Shiinaha ayaa diiradda saaraya daawooyinka caadiga ah ee daaweynta cudurada fayraska, iyadoo sagaal tijaabooyin heerka III ah lagu sameeyay remdesivir, oo lagu sameeyay dalal badan oo kala duwan, iyadoo warbixinta la filayo in la soo saaro dhammaadka Abriil.
Ilaa Abriil 2020, waxaa jira tijaabooyin joogto ah oo tijaabo ah oo loogu talagalay COVID-19 daroogada. Daawooyin badan oo caadi ah oo loo isticmaalo daaweynta cudurada fayraska ayaa la tijaabiyaa si loo hubiyo inay daaweyn karaan COVID-19, kuwaas oo ay ka mid yihiin remdesivir, chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir iyo lopinavir/ritonavir oo lagu daro interferon beta.
Bishii Abriil 2020, waxaa jira caddayn muujinaya in remdesivir uu wax ku ool yahay.
Bukaanka la daaweeyey remdesivir waxay muujiyeen waxyeelo.
Tijaabooyinka heerka III ee loo yaqaan 'Chloroquine', oo loo isticmaalo daaweynta Malaria, ayaa lagu sameeyay Febraayo 2020, waxaana la helay natiijooyin aasaasi ah.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, dadku waxay ku baaqayaan inay sameeyaan cilmi baaris dheeraad ah.
Wasaaradaha caafimaadka ee Kuuriya iyo Shiinaha waxay ku talinayaan isticmaalka chloroquine.
Hase yeeshee, Xarunta Wuhan ee Cudurka Fayraska, iyadoo ku talineysa in la isticmaalo hal garaam maalintii, waxay muujineysaa in labo jeer ee hadhuudhka ay keeni karto dhibaatooyin daran oo daawo iyo geeri.
Bishii Maarso 28, 2020, FDA waxay si ku meel gaar ah u oggolaatay dhakhaatiirta daaweynta bukaannada COVID-19 inay si qarsoodi ah u isticmaalaan hydroxychloroquine iyo chloroquine. Tilmaamaha fasalka 7 waxaa ka mid ah isticmaalka interferon, ribavirin ama umifenovir si looga hortago COVID-19.
Xogta aasaasiga ah waxay muujineysaa in qadarka ugu badan ee ribavirin loo baahan yahay si looga hortago SARS-CoV-2 oo aan u gudbin.
Nitazoxanide waxaa sidoo kale loo isticmaali karaa fayraska soo gala jirka oo dib loo eegay kadib markii la ogaaday tiro yar oo SARS-CoV-2. Daraasaddu waxay muujisay in loo baahan yahay dufanka ugu horreeya ee loo yaqaan 'Triple-type 2 receptor receptor' (TMPRSS2) si SARS-CoV-2 u galo qaataha ACE2.
Daraasadaha ku saabsan chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine oo ay ku jiraan ama aan lahayn azithromycin ayaa muujinaya caqabado adag oo ka hortag ah in la isticmaalo daawada iyada oo aan la sameynin daraasado dheeri ah. Oseltamivir ma ka saarayo SARS-CoV-2 iyada oo aan la helin wax saameyn ah oo la ogaaday daaweynta COVID-19.
Cytokines-ka ayaa sababi kara dhibaatooyinka marka COVID-19 uu bilaabo inuu noqdo mid aad u daran.
Waxaa jira caddayn muujinaya in hydroxychloroquine ay awood u leedahay inay ka hortagto cytokines. Guddiga caafimaadka ee Shiinaha ayaa Tocilizumab ku daray daawooyinka la isticmaali karo kadib daraasad yar oo la sameeyay.
Talyaaniga waxaa lagu sameeyaa tijaabo heerka 2 ah oo ay ku jiraan tijaabooyin heer qaran ah oo ka soo baxaya natiijooyinka wanaagsan ee dadka qaba cudurka.
Tijaabada dhiigga ee mugdiga ah ee lagu ogaanayo cirbadaha ayaa lagu qiimeeyaa koritaanka, taas oo u badan tahay inay sabab u tahay cirbadaha qaarkood.
Sannadkii 2017, FDA waxay ansixisay isticmaalka antagonist-ka cudurka ee interleukin-6 receptor antagonist-ka oo ku saleysan daraasado daaweyn ah oo ku saabsan cudurka steroid-ka ee sababaha kale, oo loo yaqaan 'CAR T-celinta daaweynta'.
Ilaa hadda, ma jirto wax caddayn ah oo muujinaya in tocilizumab uu wax ku ool u yahay daaweynta CRS.
